description:
Tag Line: The Whole Text Cannon; The meaning of a statute is to be looked for, not in any single section, but in all the parts together and in their relation to the end in view; Out of the two interpretations, that which ends in the furtherance of the object of the statute should be preferred to the one that would frustrate it;

Decided: 17-09-2025

Other Citations: PLD 2026 Lahore 90,2026 PTD 318 [Lahore High Court]
